<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人在寇员外家呆了一个多月。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每次他们要走，寇员外都会求他们再呆几天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于有一天吃早餐时，唐僧坚持要离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们呆在这里的话，是绝对不能取到真经的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“求你们别走。”寇员外说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们很重要。款待你们，是善行。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想呆在这里。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他咬了一口桃子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。师父是对的。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得继续西行。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人生气了。“你们真没良心！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们款待你们，照顾你们，而你们却想离开！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们非常感谢。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我们不能再呆下去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>早饭后，悟净从寇员外的马厩里牵出马来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒整理了行李。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧谢过寇员外和寇夫人后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人继续西行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些没良心的家伙！”寇夫人嘟囔道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，寇夫人跑到村子的官府。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的眼里充满泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“官府大人，我有话要说！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人哭着说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>官府大人马上跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“寇夫人！您有什么事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨晚我家进了强盗。”寇夫人气喘吁吁地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"他们偷走了值钱的东西和两匹马。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇员外想阻止他们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可那些强盗……他们……杀死了我丈夫！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人大哭起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>官府大人大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，天啊！您看见强盗们了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人抽着鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，还有，我知道他们是谁。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们是谁？”官府大人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人咬着牙说：“是唐僧和他的徒弟们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>官府大人转身对侍卫说：“带上一些人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>去抓唐僧和他的徒弟们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真高兴可以继续西行。”唐僧说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真希望快点到达西天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在寇员外家呆得太久了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒哼了一声。“应该呆得更久点。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，路前方出现了四个男人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们拿着刀和斧子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的马驮着一些大行李。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把钱交出来！”一个男人大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抽出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空。”唐僧说，“记住，不可以伤人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“我只是和他们聊聊，师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转身朝向大喊的男人。“我们没钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？没钱？”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们就得把你们都打一顿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不知道我是谁啊？我是美猴王孙悟空！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不在乎你是谁。”男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是危险的强盗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>昨晚我们抢劫了一个非常有钱的员外家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧扬起了眉毛。“员外？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空迅速念了个咒语，冻住了强盗们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净跑向马，打开了一个盒子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面有盘子、宝石，还有其他值钱的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些东西是寇员外的！马也是！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧咬了咬嘴唇。“寇员外是好人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们得把他的东西还给他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都同意了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又念另一个咒语，冰化了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变大，眼里冒火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上离开这里！”他大声说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，绝对不要再偷东西！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>强盗们大叫着逃走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人牵着寇员外的马又朝村子走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，他们看见一些官府的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>340635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都骑着马。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>347636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些官府的人是朝我们这边来的。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>347636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>351637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想知道他们要干什么。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>351637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个人用剑对准了师徒四人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>361754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“站住，小偷们！我要把你们都抓起来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>